#US #COVID19 #vaccine Vaccine update for 1/12. Another 2.2 MM doses received by the states, less than 800,000 administered. down to 35.9% used. ND running #1, up there with WV/SD/CT. 

NJ still ~30th in the US, running below the bottom half. Still No info on demographics. https://t.co/3jbKjdeY4I
